  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to test the utility of the nasogastric tube, which is used to
      decompress and as &quot;guardian&quot; of gastro-jejunal anastomosis, in patients undergoing distal
      subtotal gastrectomy for gastric cancer with reconstruction according to Billroth II or
      according Roux.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A silastic naso-gastric tube (Rusch速 distributed by Teleflex Medical Srl) is used in the
      naso-gastric/jejunal tube group
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
